Hey.. this is the last time im gonna play with this for like a month most likely.  So most of you know I'm goin to Idaho for all of July to visit my Dad and the rest of my family I left behind.  But for once I actually don't want to leave.  I'm gonna miss you all so much.  Andrea, we've been through so much together, but we're still together.  Hopefull it stays like that forever.  I love you sooooo much and you have no idea how much I'm gonna miss you.  I'll call you EVERYDAY i can tho.  So as happy as I am to leave, it's also killin me.  I don't want to, but I still do.  Ya know what I mean?  It's bittersweet.  I get to see my Dad, but I dont get to be bored and hang out with Chris everyday.  I get to see my grandparents, but I dont get to tell Jen all of my problems.  I get to see my Great Grandma.. but I dont get to hang out with my bestest pal Elisabitch (jk, i love you, u know that).  So there is my heart felt good bye thing.  So if I dont play with this thing again for a while, I love you, and see ya in a month.

[josh]

Ok.. so that was totally fucked up... I'm never listening to other ppl again.  So yeah.. I love you soooooooooooooo much andrea, you have no idea, and im so glad that we talked and worked everything out.  I'll miss you this summmer :(
